{"meta":{"title":"ZengDaLin","subtitle":"ZengDaLin","description":"","author":"ZengDaLin","url":"http://example.com","root":"/"},"pages":[{"title":"friends","date":"2022-03-27T12:27:36.000Z","updated":"2022-03-27T12:28:10.343Z","comments":true,"path":"friends/index.html","permalink":"http://example.com/friends/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"about","date":"2022-03-27T12:14:36.000Z","updated":"2022-03-27T12:16:28.040Z","comments":true,"path":"about/index.html","permalink":"http://example.com/about/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"tags","date":"2022-03-27T03:10:28.000Z","updated":"2022-03-27T12:24:02.984Z","comments":true,"path":"tags/index.html","permalink":"http://example.com/tags/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"categories","date":"2022-03-27T03:13:08.000Z","updated":"2022-03-27T03:27:26.133Z","comments":false,"path":"categories/index.html","permalink":"http://example.com/categories/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"404","date":"2022-03-27T12:31:56.000Z","updated":"2022-03-27T12:32:17.921Z","comments":true,"path":"404/index.html","permalink":"http://example.com/404/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"contact","date":"2022-03-27T12:24:32.000Z","updated":"2022-03-27T12:24:55.719Z","comments":true,"path":"contact/index.html","permalink":"http://example.com/contact/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""}],"posts":[{"title":"止盈与止损和盈亏比","slug":"盈亏比","date":"2022-03-29T13:53:03.000Z","updated":"2022-04-05T15:21:37.286Z","comments":true,"path":"2022/03/29/ying-yu-bi/","link":"","permalink":"http://example.com/2022/03/29/ying-yu-bi/","excerpt":"","text":"做交易的时候，建议先设置止盈价和止损价。通常，盈亏比(止盈价-开仓价/开仓价-止损价)需要大于3。如何能做到高的盈亏比和较好的胜率，可以有下面的方法：1.开仓价离支撑价近(如长期均线支撑价或前期反复测试的低点或整数点位等等(大家都认为是支撑的地方，才是支撑。思考价格是否为支撑位，需要从其他人的角度))，2.止损价设在支撑价。因为大家都会在支撑价做止损，如果一旦跌破，止损盘会带来卖压3.根据开仓价和止损价，再根据盈亏比需要大于3的原则，算出最低的止盈价4.这样的方法，可以保护你的本金，即使亏损，因为你的开仓价与止损价设的近，也会亏得少5.选强势的，走牛市的标的(这样的标的胜率高，就是有更大的可能性能达到止盈价)。6.如果达到止盈价，如果你还不满意，想继续持有，可以考虑一下当前这个标的的市场情绪(当然这个非常难判断)。如果想继续持有，可以把止损价设在原来的止损价上，以便保护收益","categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"交易概念","slug":"交易概念","permalink":"http://example.com/tags/%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5/"}]},{"title":"Hello World","slug":"hello-world","date":"2022-03-27T03:05:34.832Z","updated":"2022-03-27T03:05:34.832Z","comments":true,"path":"2022/03/27/hello-world/","link":"","permalink":"http://example.com/2022/03/27/hello-world/","excerpt":"","text":"Welcome to Hexo! This is your very first post. Check documentation for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in troubleshooting or you can ask me on GitHub. Quick StartCreate a new post$ hexo new \"My New Post\" More info: Writing Run server$ hexo server More info: Server Generate static files$ hexo generate More info: Generating Deploy to remote sites$ hexo deploy More info: Deployment","categories":[],"tags":[]}],"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"交易概念","slug":"交易概念","permalink":"http://example.com/tags/%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5/"}]}